{
  "texts": [
    "Based on the findings of our review, we identify understudied areas and future research opportunities using text analysis in blockchain research.",
    "This allows researchers to recognize promising research topics and specify the methodologies (and data) they can use.",
    "Initial keyword searches were conducted on May 24, 2022, followed by updated searches on August 23, 2022, to find relevant studies.",
    "We chose the Web of Science (WoS) and Scopus databases to cover publications indexed in academic databases.",
    "As text analysis in blockchain research is relatively new, some studies may not have been published."
  ]
}